{"tid":1680202,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(1031)想大家一齊放低傷心 輕鬆一晚嘅都入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-28T16:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T17:44:15.000Z","uid":309825,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9596cb5d40f7bc6a2329114d2a544f7279fe347c","tid":1680202,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">10月31日有唔少活動</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雖然大家831依然好傷痛 但係我地更加要話俾黑警知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢咁樣係唔會令到我地驚架</span><br />\n無錯 我地會傷心 不過我地會將悲痛化為力量<br />\n仲好快就可以走出陰霾</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">不如大家一齊放低傷心 輕鬆一晚<br />\n打扮做自己鍾意嘅卡通人物 電影角色 動漫角色等<br />\n享受一晚 chill一晚<br />\n之後11月2日 各路手足再show time</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 7PM 太子站兩個月悼念</span></strong></strong></strong><br />\n太子恐怖襲擊事件已經過左兩個月，香港人唔會忘記<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">個人認為唔應該再分散去咁多個地鐵站，上次21號已經試過唔夠人，試吓喺周圍嘅球場到舉行，千奇唔好喺狗屋度搞</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 7:30PM 維園集合行去蘭桂坊</span></strong></strong></strong><br />\n創意抗爭，黎個靜坐/小型遊行，反對禁蒙面法，又影響下蘭桂坊生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞手：<a href=\"https://t.me/MasqueradeHalloween1031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FMasqueradeHalloween1031&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=dad6a08c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/MasqueradeHalloween1031</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 9:30AM 海洋公園正門售票處，光復OP</span></strong></strong></strong><br />\n手足因應海洋公園政治打壓而發起既活動，順手係到呼籲大家一定要罷去OP HALLOWEEN，特別請南區街坊多多支持<br />\n[光復op] 做op halloween自問有良知嘅同我死晒入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1679155/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1679155/page/1</a><br />\n海洋公園跪低 自我政治審查<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1675991/page/1\" data-auto-l